nodes.text: An individual was involved in the last hunt and in the death of the bounty hunter Janna Relasi. Relasi lived long enough to contact her droid, GSAD-43, and ordered the droid to "get them for me." GSAD-43 used the onboard computer of Janna Relasi's ship and through her research, found enough clues to discover the identity of one of the culprits — although GSAD-43 assumed that there were other involved co-conspirators. GSAD-43 upgraded her weaponry, tracked the murderer, and took that individual to justice.
